	<section class="about-page" aria-labelledby="about-title">
		<div class="container about-inner">
			<header class="page-heading">
				<h1 id="about-title">About</h1>
				<p>I am a technology and operations leader with more than two decades of experience building software, products, teams, and programs.</p>
				<ul class="social-handles about-social-handles">
					<li>
						<a href="https://github.com/solankydev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="GitHub" title="GitHub">
